OL,3,C'Please reconsider': The impact of
OL,4,CTrump's aid cuts on those who need it
OL,5,Cmost
OL,7,FITV News Asia Correspondent Debi
OL,8,FEdward travelled to the Myanmar-
OL,9,FThailand border to see how the funding
OL,10,Fcuts are impacting refugees there
OL,12,FThe Tha Song Yang Hospital already
OL,13,Fserves a large Thai community close to
OL,14,Fthe border with Myanmar, but since US
OL,15,Faid was cut to clinics inside a nearby
OL,16,Frefugee camp, their waiting room has
OL,17,Fbecome even more crowded.
