OL,7,FOn the day we visited, there were
OL,8,Fseveral Burmese refugees seeking
OL,9,Fmedical help, including Cho Aye, who
OL,10,Fis suffering from a nerve disease.
OL,12,FThe 44-year-old was wincing in pain as
OL,13,Fshe waited to be seen by a doctor,
OL,14,Fshe'd been told she could no longer
OL,15,Fget some of the medicine she needed to
OL,16,Fcontrol her symptoms, and her
OL,17,Fdiscomfort.
