OL,7,FShe told us that in the past the
OL,8,Fsupport in the camp clinics had been
OL,9,Fgreat, but since their closure, she's
OL,10,Fbeen suffering in pain, without the
OL,11,Fmedications she needs.
OL,13,FThe maternity clinic has been one of
OL,14,Fthe hardest hit, with women no longer
OL,15,Fable to receive care in the camps.
OL,17,FWaiting in line we met Moi Ei San who
OL,18,Fis eight months pregnant.
