OL,7,FShe had fled the war in Myanmar to
OL,8,Fhave her baby in the safety of a
OL,9,Frefugee camp where her grandmother was
OL,10,Falready living.
OL,12,FIt was going to be free to deliver in
OL,13,Fthe camp, but she'd just been told
OL,14,Fshe'd have to pay a fee in the Thai
OL,15,Fhospital.
OL,17,FShe broke down in tears, telling me
OL,18,Fshe didn't have any money and didn't
OL,19,Fknow what to do.
