OL,8,Fher hometown in Myanmar because she
OL,9,Fknows she will get free care there,
OL,10,Fbut it would mean having to return to
OL,11,Fa conflict zone.
OL,13,FIn 2024, the US accounted for almost
OL,14,Fhalf of global humanitarian aid.
OL,16,FOn his first day in office, President
OL,17,FDonald Trump ordered a 90-day freeze
OL,18,Fof all US foreign aid and a review of
OL,19,Faid policy.
