OL,3,C'Please reconsider': The impact of
OL,4,CTrump's aid cuts on those who need it
OL,5,Cmost
OL,7,FElon Musk's DOGE department followed
OL,8,Fup with a freeze on USAID payments and
OL,9,Ftold most of its staff that they were
OL,10,Fbeing placed on leave, locking them
OL,11,Fout of their emails.
OL,13,FIt meant that overnight people working
OL,14,Ffor USAID were forced to down tools
OL,15,Fand cease operations.
OL,17,FThe suspension of that work, and the
OL,18,Ffunding behind it, has thrown the
OL,19,Fsupport system for Burmese refugees
OL,20,Finto chaos.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
