OL,7,FDoctors from the Tha Song Yang
OL,8,FHospital have started going into the
OL,9,Frefugee camps, on a voluntary basis,
OL,10,Fto continue the disease prevention
OL,11,Fprogrammes, which until recently had
OL,12,Fbeen supported by USAID.
OL,14,FMalaria, Cholera and Tuberculosis (TB)
OL,15,Fhave all been prevalent in the border
OL,16,Fregion, even more so since the Myanmar
OL,17,Fconflict began in 2021.
OL,19,FWe visited one remote TB clinic where
OL,20,Fcases continue to rise.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
