OL,7,FThey had started talking to the US
OL,8,Fgovernment and USAID about supporting
OL,9,Fa simple walkie-talkie system that
OL,10,Fwould work through FM radio and allow
OL,11,Fvillages to communicate with one
OL,12,Fanother and warn each other if jets or
OL,13,Fdrones were heard in the area.
OL,15,FThere is no phone reception in these
OL,16,Fjungle areas so the walkie-talkie
OL,17,Fradio system would have been a
OL,18,Flifesaver.
OL,20,FBut now, they won't have any funding
OL,21,Fto help them set it up.
