OL,7,FWe did speak to some aid workers on
OL,8,Fthe Thai-Myanmar border who said in
OL,9,Fthe long term it could be good for the
OL,10,Fhumanitarian aid system to be
OL,11,Frecalibrated, that maybe it was time
OL,12,Ffor the local governments in the
OL,13,Faffected places, to take a stronger
OL,14,Flead.
OL,16,FHowever they also expressed concern
OL,17,Fabout the number of countries,
OL,18,Fincluding the UK, which are planning
OL,19,Faid cuts, and what that means in the
OL,20,Fshort-term.
