OL,7,FAt the Mae Tao clinic in Mae Sot, they
OL,8,Fsay food supplies, education, mental
OL,9,Fhealth care and rehab for bombing
OL,10,Fvictims are all part of the
OL,11,Fhumanitarian support system that is
OL,12,Fnow under threat.
OL,14,FThe director of the clinic, Dr Cynthia
OL,15,FMaung, has been running her facility
OL,16,Ffor 30 years. She is discussing
OL,17,Fsolutions to the aid cuts with the
OL,18,FThai Government and the network of
OL,19,FNGOs which work in the area.
